            "game-obj": "Traits",
            "type": "alternate_link"
          },
          "classes": [
            "creature_type"
          ],
          "edition": "remastered",
          "game-id": "651e06f09e5aea780d7c70a36ce5b1f2",
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "name": "Plant",
          "sources": [
            {
              "errata": {
                "alt": "2.0",
                "aonid": 216,
                "game-obj": "Sources",
                "name": "2.0",
                "type": "link"
              },
              "link": {
                "alt": "Player Core pg. 459",
                "aonid": 216,
                "game-obj": "Sources",
                "name": "Player Core pg. 459",
                "type": "link"
              },
              "name": "Player Core",
              "page": 459,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "text": "Vegetable creatures have the plant trait. They are distinct from normal plants. Magical effects with this trait manipulate or conjure plants or plant matter in some way. Effects that manipulate plants have no effect in an area with no plants.",
          "type": "trait"
        },
        {
          "classes": [
            "monsters"
          ],
          "edition": "remastered",
          "game-id": "7c548a9e0a2647c082989720b3de0a87",
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "name": "Wood",
          "sources": [
            {
              "errata": {
                "alt": "2.0",
                "aonid": 216,
                "game-obj": "Sources",
                "name": "2.0",
                "type": "link"
              },
              "link": {
                "alt": "Player Core pg. 463",
                "aonid": 216,
                "game-obj": "Sources",
                "name": "Player Core pg. 463",
                "type": "link"
              },
              "name": "Player Core",
              "page": 463,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "text": "Effects with the wood trait conjure or manipulate wood. Those that manipulate wood have no effect in an area without wood. Creatures with this trait consist primarily of wood or have a connection to magical wood.  \n  \nThese planes consist of trees and other flora latticed in organic patterns. Wood planes are often perfectly constructed to match their desired purpose or environment but aren\u2019t usually outright hostile to visitors.",
          "type": "trait"
        }
      ],
      "type": "stat_block_section"
    },
